<MELItem itemNbr="34-42-02" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-34-42-02.1.2-34-42-02_FAA">
<Title>Traffic Collision and Avoidance System (TCAS)</Title>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="A" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="1">
<Title>One Inoperative (*)</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One may be inoperative.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
</DispatchCondition>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="B" repairInterval="B" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="0">
<Title>Both Inoperative</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Both may be inoperative provided that:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Aircraft operates within Vietnam's airspace only, and </Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Before flight, ATC must be advised of the unserviceable TCAS and TCAS INOP must be indicated in the item 18 RMK of ATC Flight Plan, and.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>If the aircraft is intended to be flown in airspace / country in which TCAS is required, the condition of dispatch in the TCAS Supplement is applied. Refer to Route manual - 2.4.4.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
</DispatchItems>